Welcome to Armature
Armature allows you to easily create wireframes
from a single Inkscape document.
This layer contains a list of each layer set that has
been created in this document.
You may hide this layer, but if you delete
it your layer set data will be lost.
To turn layers on or off, simply add or
remove their names from the list of layers.
To replace an existing layer set, create a
new layer set with the same name as the
one you would like to replace.
To turn layers on or off, simply add or
remove their names from the list of layers.
